        "Cao Hoang Du" to "<p><u><strong>CAO HOANG DU : </strong></u><u><strong>膏肓俞 </strong></u><u><strong>B&Agrave;NG QUANG 43</strong></u></p>\n" +
                "<table width=\"1200\">\n" +
