        "Ngoại Quan" to "<p><u><strong>NGOẠI QUAN: </strong></u><u><strong>外關 </strong></u><u><strong>TAM TI&Ecirc;U 05</strong></u></p>\n" +
                "<table width=\"1200\">\n" +
                "<tbody>\n" +
                "<tr>\n" +
                "<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"1200\">\n" +
