        "Khê Mạch" to "<p><u><strong>KH&Ecirc; MẠCH: </strong></u><u><strong>瘛脈</strong></u><u><strong>-</strong></u><u><strong>瘈脈 </strong></u><u><strong>TAM TI&Ecirc;U 18</strong></u></p>\n" +
